/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/26\/hadith-on-mosques-the-masjid-was-only-built-to-remember-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":7195,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: The Masjid was only built to remember Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Buraydah reported: A man announced loudly in the mosque, saying, \u201cHas anyone seen my red camel?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMay you not find it! Verily, the mosques were only built for the purpose they were built.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 569 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13995,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/06\/every-step-mosque-rewarded\/","url_meta":{"origin":7195,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: Every step to mosque for prayer is rewarded","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever purifies himself with ablution in his house, then he walks to a house among the houses of Allah to fulfill an obligation among the obligations of Allah, one step of his will expiate his sins\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15891,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/29\/more-reward-walk-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":7195,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: More reward for walking to the Masjid","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: A plot of land around the mosque was vacant, so the tribe of Salimah intended to move there to be closer to the mosque. The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was told about that and he said to them, \"I have heard that you\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11568,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/jannah-salat-fil-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":7195,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: Paradise for regular Masjid attendance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever comes and goes between the mosque, Allah will prepare his place in Paradise every time he comes and goes.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 662, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 669 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42588,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/02\/counted-every-step\/","url_meta":{"origin":7195,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Masjid: Allah counted every step as a reward","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 2, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ubayy ibn Ka\u2019b reported: There was a man who lived the furthest from the mosque, as far as I know. He never missed a congregational prayer. It was said to him, \u201cIf you buy a donkey, you can ride it during the dark nights and hot days.\u201d The man said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14009,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/06\/waiting-prayer-fortress\/","url_meta":{"origin":7195,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Masjid: Waiting for consecutive prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cShall I not tell you of a deed by which Allah expiates your sins and raises your status?\u201d They said, \u201cOf course, O Messenger of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThorough ablution despite difficulty, taking many steps\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7195","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"re